Monkey Boards 0.4

Requirements

* Web server
* PHP version 5.0.0 or later
* SQLite support enabled in PHP

Installation

1. Copy everything in /upload to a directory on your web server.
2. Browse to it with your web browser, e.g. http://mydomain.com/monkeyboards/.
3. You should see the "Monkey Boards Installation" page. Follow the instructions.
